@dafukSpin_HostAddress = http://localhost:5244

# dafukSpin MyAnimeList API Endpoints

## Health Check
### Health Check
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

## User Anime Lists

### Get User's Anime List with Custom Filter
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/users/testuser/anime?status=watching&limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User's Completed Anime
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/users/testuser/anime/completed?limit=10&sort=list_updated_at
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User's Currently Watching Anime
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/users/testuser/anime/watching?limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User's Plan to Watch Anime
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/users/testuser/anime/plan-to-watch?limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User's On Hold Anime
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/users/testuser/anime/on-hold
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User's Dropped Anime
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/users/testuser/anime/dropped
Accept: application/json

###

## Anime Details & Search

### Get Anime Details by ID
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/details/5114
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Anime by Query
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/search?query=attack%20on%20titan&limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Anime - Naruto
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/search?query=naruto&limit=3
Accept: application/json

###

## Discovery & Rankings

### Get Anime Rankings - All
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/ranking?rankingType=all&limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Anime Rankings - TV Series
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/ranking?rankingType=tv&limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Anime Rankings - Movies
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/ranking?rankingType=movie&limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Seasonal Anime - Spring 2024
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/seasonal/2024/spring?limit=10&sort=anime_score
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Seasonal Anime - Fall 2023
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/seasonal/2023/fall?limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Suggested Anime
GET {{dafukSpin_HostAddress}}/api/anime/suggestions?limit=10
Accept: application/json

